ed="T" n="0794c16"/><persName key="A010820">釋秀公</persName>者，<placeName key="PL000000026549">齊安</placeName>人也。髫年天然有離俗之<lb
ed="T" n="0794c17"/>意焉。既丁荼蓼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g905"/>，便往<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀<anchor xml:id="beg0794003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>郡</sic><corr>部</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0794003"/></placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0794sgsz6"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0794sgsz6"/><persName key="A006502">興<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，諷<lb
ed="T" n="0794c18"/>誦經典，易若溫尋<ptr type="glossary" target="#g330"/>。又依之進具，果通達毘<lb
ed="T" n="0794c19"/>尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>，乃為<persName key="A006502">興<roleName>公</roleName></persName>傳律上足弟子歟！如是四載，<lb
ed="T" n="0794c20"/>入<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>，造<persName key="A001519">宣<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>門，為依止<ptr type="glossary" target="#g333"/>之客。勤以忘<lb
ed="T" n="0794c21"/>勞，涉十六年，不離函丈<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1025"/>。窮幽諸部，陶練<lb
ed="T" n="0794c22"/>數家，將<persName key="A001269">首</persName>疏為宗本，然向<placeName key="PL000000026549">黃州</placeName>報所生<lb
ed="T" n="0794c23"/>地。次往<placeName key="PL000000027682">安陸</placeName>，大揚講訓。聲美所聞，諸王牧<lb
ed="T" n="0794c24"/>守攸共遵承正化，緇徒咸摹細行。有<persName key="A010822">貞固<lb
ed="T" n="0794c25"/><roleName>律師</roleName></persName>居<anchor xml:id="begd1e23560"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e23560"/>上席；解冠諸生最顯清名；餘皆<lb
ed="T" n="0794c26"/>後殿。其諸成業，不可勝算。春秋七十餘，卒<lb
ed="T" n="0794c27"/><anchor xml:id="begd1e23570"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e23570"/><placeName key="PL000000027661">十力寺</placeName>本房焉。</p>
